# LIMS — Logbook Internship Management System

## 1. Project Identity

- **Name:** LIMS (Logbook Internship Management System)
- **Type:** Final Year Project (FYP) — Faculty of Computing
- **Purpose:** Digitize internship logbook management for students and supervisors. Students submit daily log entries; supervisors review, approve, or reject them.
- **Live URL:** https://lim-system.my/
- **Repository:** https://github.com/IAreShut/Ipan
- **Local Path:** `C:\Users\User\FYP System\Ipan`

