## 3. Architecture & Conventions

### MVC Structure

- **Controller-per-role** pattern: `AuthController`, `StudentController`, `SupervisorController`
- No dedicated Form Request classes — validation is inline in controller methods
- No role-based middleware — authorization checks are done inside controller methods using `Auth::user()->role` or ownership checks
- `AppServiceProvider` forces HTTPS in production via `URL::forceScheme('https')`

### Route Organisation

Routes are grouped by role prefix with named route convention:

```
/                       → welcome (landing page)
/login, /register       → AuthController
/student/*              → StudentController  (name: student.*)
/supervisor/*           → SupervisorController (name: supervisor.*)
/admin/*                → placeholder (Coming Soon)
```

All authenticated routes use `middleware(['auth'])`.

### Eloquent Models (7 total)

| Model                  | Table                    | Key Relationships                                                                          |
| ---------------------- | ------------------------ | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------ |
| `User`                 | `users`                  | hasMany LogEntry, hasMany Internship, belongsTo User (supervisor), hasMany User (students) |
| `Internship`           | `internships`            | belongsTo User (student), hasMany LogEntry                                                 |
| `LogEntry`             | `log_entries`            | belongsTo User (student), belongsTo Internship, hasMany LogAttachment                      |
| `LogAttachment`        | `log_attachments`        | belongsTo LogEntry                                                                         |
| `Notification`         | `notifications`          | belongsTo User                                                                             |
| `Task`                 | `tasks`                  | belongsTo User (user), belongsTo User (creator)                                            |
| `SupervisorAssignment` | `supervisor_assignments` | Lookup table for pre-assigned student-supervisor matching                                  |

### Blade View Structure

```
resources/views/
├── auth/
│   └── login.blade.php
├── layouts/
│   ├── app.blade.php
│   └── master.blade.php
├── student/
│   ├── dashboard.blade.php
│   ├── log-entries.blade.php
│   ├── log-entry-show.blade.php
│   ├── notifications.blade.php
│   ├── profile.blade.php
│   ├── progress.blade.php
│   └── progress-week.blade.php
├── supervisor/
│   ├── analytics.blade.php
│   ├── dashboard.blade.php
│   ├── milestones.blade.php
│   └── review-logbook.blade.php
└── welcome.blade.php
```

