## 4. Database Schema

### users

- `id`, `name`, `email`, `password`, `role` (student/supervisor/admin)
- `company`, `supervisor_id` (self-referencing FK → users.id)
- `matrix_id`, `phone` (+60 format), `faculty`, `class`, `programme_code`, `location`, `about`, `avatar`
- `email_verified_at`, `remember_token`, timestamps

### internships

- `id`, `student_id` (FK → users.id)
- `company_name`, `company_address`, `start_date`, `end_date`, `total_weeks`
- timestamps

### log_entries

- `id`, `student_id` (FK → users.id), `internship_id` (FK → internships.id)
- `entry_date` (date), `week_number` (integer)
- `task_description` (text), `ai_summary` (text, nullable)
- `status`: `draft` → `pending` → `approved` / `rejected`
- `supervisor_comment` (text, nullable)
- timestamps

### log_attachments

- `id`, `log_entry_id` (FK → log_entries.id)
- `file_path` (Cloudinary URL or local asset URL), `file_name`, `file_type`
- timestamps

### notifications (custom — NOT Laravel's default)

- `id`, `user_id` (FK → users.id)
- `title`, `message`, `type` (info/reminder/milestone/etc.), `is_read` (boolean)
- timestamps

### supervisor_assignments

- `student_matrix_id` (string, unique), `student_name`, `supervisor_matrix_id`
- `faculty`, `programme_code`, `class` — academic info for auto-fill during registration
- timestamps
- `id`, `user_id` (FK → users.id), `created_by` (FK → users.id)
- `title`, `due_date` (datetime), `type` (sv_milestone / personal_reminder)
- timestamps

